## Implementation Impact

### What changes from the current sandbox

| Component | Current | Correct |
|-----------|---------|---------|
| `AdsCampaign.cost` | Total (aggregate) | Keep as aggregate for display, but NOT for daily calculation |
| **NEW: `CampaignDailyMetric[]`** | Not exists | Daily cache — source of truth for per-day cost |
| `generateDailyMockData()` | Distributes campaign totals across days | Looks up actual cached daily data per campaign |
| Ledger | Determines which campaigns are "active" per day | Same — no change |
| Ref counts | Daily per link ref | Same — no change |

### New Mock Data Needed

```typescript
// Instead of campaign.cost = 3_000_000 (total)
// Generate realistic daily breakdown:
function generateMockDailyCache(campaign: AdsCampaign, startDate: string, days: number): CampaignDailyMetric[] {
  const dailyAvgCost = campaign.cost / days;
  return Array.from({ length: days }, (_, i) => {
    const date = addDays(startDate, i);
    const jitter = 0.6 + Math.random() * 0.8; // ±40% daily variation
    return {
      campaignId: campaign.id,
      date,
      cost: Math.round(dailyAvgCost * jitter),
      clicks: Math.round((campaign.clicks / days) * jitter),
      impressions: Math.round((campaign.impressions / days) * jitter),
      conversions: Math.round((campaign.conversions / days) * jitter),
    };
  });
}
```

